Build Guidance
==============


Quick start:
------------

[Install dependencies]
sudo apt-get install build-essential libglib2.0-dev libncurses-dev uuid-dev libjson-c-dev

[Build]
make

[Install]
sudo make install


Build deb packages:
-------------------

[Install dependencies]
sudo apt-get install build-essential libglib2.0-dev libncurses-dev uuid-dev libjson-c-dev dev devscripts build-essential lintian debhelper

[Build]
debuild -b #vm-manager_x.x.x_amd64.deb will be generated at parent directory

[Install]
dpkg -i vm-manager_x.x.x_amd64.deb
